| 🟡 Medium | No rate limiting | Denial of service |
| 🟡 Medium | No CORS configuration | Cross-origin abuse |
| 🟡 Medium | No input validation framework | Injection attacks |
| 🟢 Low | Hardcoded port | Deployment inflexibility |
| 🟢 Low | No graceful shutdown | Dropped connections |

